    <stitle>7 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER SERIES - REMOVE - CLUTCH HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="1">
        <title>CLUTCH HOUSING</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">For models so equipped, remove the clutch release mechanism and/or clutch brake assembly.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the four bolts and six nuts from the studs (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302510">left, Figure 10</hotlnk>). Jar clutch housing with a rubber mallet to break
                the gasket seal and pull from the transmission case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302510">right, Figure 10</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302510" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302510" filename="../figg13/g1302510.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 10. Remove Bolts and Nuts, and Pull Clutch Housing From Transmission Case</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
